AgileWizard use Rake as build tool and ruby as language for build script. Documentation of Rake at http://docs.rubyrake.org/
Ruby 1.9.2 & ruby_devkit are required.
Please download ruby and devkit from http://rubyinstaller.org/.
And you can find method to install ruby devkit at https://github.com/oneclick/rubyinstaller/wiki/Development-Kit.

Please install albacore version 0.2.0 which under this directory.

Note: No blank char allowed in ruby installed directory, or you can not install ruby extension 'jekyll'.